Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.57,Dialogue_JPN,对白 JP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}まさか奴が！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.83,Dialogue_JPN,对白 JP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敵艦フォールドします
